('5', 'Motorcycle Technician - VISA Sponsorship Available.', '<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">About us</span></b></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Neguinho Motors is one of the UK\'s fastest growing motorcycle shop.</span></p>\n\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\"> </span></b></p>\n\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Full job description</span></b></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">The opportunity to join a friendly team and develop your existing career as a <b><i>Motorcycle Technician </i></b>within <b><i>Neguinho Motors</i></b>.\n We believe that by identifying your potential and investing in your \nfuture, you will be able to develop skills and gain the experience that \nwill enrich your career prospects.</span></p>\n\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\"> </span></b></p>\n\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Salary – £30,000 – £36,234 per year</span></b></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Preferential for servicing, MOTs and parts</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Fantastic discounts on vehicles sales</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Pension scheme</span></p>\n\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Sponsorship scheme available. </span></b></p>\n\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\"> </span></b></p>\n\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Job Role</span></b></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">You\n will carry out inspections and service routines, repairs and testing of\n vehicles in a professional and safe manner, meeting manufacture \nstandards and timeframes as required, contributing to an outstanding \nGuest Experience.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Test and diagnose vehicle faults, interpreting repair order instructions and technical information.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Plan necessary work and order parts to ensure vehicles are ready as promptly as possible.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Carry\n out all servicing and repairs as per manufacturer standards and with \neffective use of time and resources, using appropriate vehicle \nprotection.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Discuss any work requiring specialist skills with the Workshop Supervisor/Controller.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Accurately\n report vehicle faults and work carried out for ease of reference by \nservice reception, including detailed actions carried out.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Observe relevant health and safety procedures, including the use of protective clothing and equipment.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Maintain working area, tools and equipment in a safe and clean condition.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Maintain correct warranty procedures and clocking details in line with defined company procedures.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Return all exchanged parts to the Parts department.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Recover defective or damaged vehicles in line with the Supervisor’s instructions.</span></p>\n\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\"> </span></b></p>\n\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Work Pattern</span></b></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, serif, EmojiFont;color:rgb(89,89,89);background-color